Version 2019.03 (2019-03-22)
  Friendica Core:
    Update to the translation (CS, DE, EN-GB, EN-US, ES, FR, IT, PL, SV, ZH-CN) [translation teams]
    Update to the documentation [Aditoo17, JeroenED, m4sk1n, softmetz, tobiasd]
